stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> created: human files issue<br/>or agent spawns subtask
    created --> assigned: orchestrator picks agent
    assigned --> accepted: adapter acks (< 1s SLA)
    assigned --> rejected: adapter cannot accept
    accepted --> working: invocation starts
    working --> working: progress events (0..N)
    working --> verifying: output ready, verification.required = true
    working --> completed: output ready, no verification
    verifying --> completed: verifier passes
    verifying --> failed: verifier fails
    working --> failed: timeout or error
    working --> input_required: agent needs input
    input_required --> working: input received
    accepted --> cancelled: control message
    working --> cancelled: control message
    rejected --> [*]
    completed --> [*]
    failed --> [*]
    cancelled --> [*]
